{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund and build air raid sirens system for civil defence",
        "additional_details": "The Emergency Alert System relies on mobile networks & internet infrastructure - which would fail in the event of:\r\n \r\n- A cyber attack on communications networks\r\n- An EMP strike\r\n \r\nWe believe that air raid sirens are a basic survival tool in an age where threats move faster than politics. We want the Government to take national survival seriously, protect Britain and act now.",
        "background": "We want the Government to build a nationwide air raid/civil defence siren system in every town and city and test it regularly.",
